title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 5 categories of Movie on the x axis representing 2 groups: North America, and Worldwide.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Movie Jurassic World with a mean value of 1161.99.
Followed by Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom with a mean value of 860.78.
The lowest category is observed at Jurassic Park III that has a mean value of 274.99
showing a difference of 123.5% with the maximum value.
In case of Jurassic World, North America shows more dominance than any other Movie and it has the lowest value in Jurassic Park III.
